    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Summary : </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oakley the Leafbug is a fast-paced 2.5D platformer built in Godot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283430/extras/170857d41877765337424a4d96d41f1a.poster.avif?t=1758827348\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283430/extras/170857d41877765337424a4d96d41f1a.webm?t=1758827348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283430/extras/170857d41877765337424a4d96d41f1a.mp4?t=1758827348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features :</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2 Playable Characters (Oakley the Leafbug &amp; Snowblitz the Arctic Fox)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drift on Oakley's leaf to surf waves and kickflip your way into gaining more speed!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Snowblitz can swap between two control sets, roll mode and trick  mode to chain combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2 Zone Types (Race &amp; Score Attack)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race : Get to the finish line as fast as possible to complete the zone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Score Attack : Score enough points to pass all score gates to complete the zone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
